4

Tìm kieám treân baûn ñoà

Tra cöùu

Hieån thò baøn ñoà thaønh phoá vaø cho pheùp thao taùc treân baûn ñoà

Caùc thao taùc thöïc hieän: phoùng to, thu nhoû baûn ñoà vaø tìm kieám ñòa danh

5

Tìm kieám ñòa danh theo chæ muïc

Tra cöùu

Cho pheùp thöïc hieän thao taùc tra cöùu ñeå tìm kieám ñòa danh döïa treân moät soá tieâu chuaån tìm kieám ñaõ ñònh ra

Keát quaû traû veà: danh saùch caùc ñòa danh thoûa caùc tieâu chuaån tìm kieám

6

Tìm kieám ñòa danh theo loaïi ñòa danh

Tra cöùu

Choïn hieån thò caùc danh saùch ñòa danh theo loaïi ñòa danh vaø ñaëc tröng cuûa töøng loaïi ñòa danh

Choïn danh saùch ñòa danh theo nhöõng muïc ñaõ lieät keâ

7

Danh saùch tuyeán tham quan

Baùo bieåu

Danh saùch caùc tuyeán tham quan coù saün trong cô sôû döõ lieäu

Do soá löôïng töông ñoái ít neân chuùng ta chæ caàn danh saùch maø khoâng caàn thöïc hieän vieäc tìm kieám tuyeán tham quan

8

Ñaêng nhaäp heä thoáng

 

Cho pheùp ngöôøi duøng (coù quyeàn quaûn tròù) ñaêng nhaäp vaøo heä thoáng

Ñaêng nhaäp vaøo heä thoáng ñeå truy xuaát vaø caäp nhaät treân cô sôû döõ lieäu goác

9

Heä thoáng quaûn lyù

10

Lieân keát caùc website khaùc

 

Danh saùch caùc website du lòch khaùc coù treân Internet

Caùc thao taùc caäp nhaät cho ñòa danh nhö: theâm, xoùa, hieäu chænh vò trí ñòa danh treân baûn ñoà

* Maøn hình Caäp nhaät ñòa danh

-         Thöïc hieän cho caùc chöùc naêng caäp nhaät ñòa danh nhö theâm, xoùa, söûa ñòa danh.

-         Bao goàm ba maøn hình lieân tieáp vaø truy xuaát laãn nhau: thoâng tin ñòa danh, thoâng tin giôùi thieäu toång quaùt veà ñòa danh vaø caùc ñaëc tröng cuûa loaïi ñòa danh töông öùng vôùi loaïi ñòa danh ñaõ choïn.

VD: maøn hình treân, ñòa danh ñang choïn laø nôi ôû (places to stay) neân ñaëc tröng phaân loaïi laø kieåu nôi ôû (design)

6

Truy xuaát ñeán maøn hình caäp nhaät hay theâm thoâng tin töông öùng vôùi töøng loaïi löïa choïn

Caùc maøn hình truy xuaát ñeå löïa choïn thoâng tin töông öùng nhö: vò trí ñòa danh treân baûn ñoà, hình aûnh, aâm thanh

. neáu ngöôøi duøng choïn xoùa hay söûa thì quay veà maøn hình baùo bieåu theå hieän danh saùch caùc ñòa danh ñaõ choïn tröôùc ñoù

o       Xoùa thoâng tin ñòa danh.

Ctrl + chuoät traùi

7

Nhaán chuoät traùi

Di chuyeån baûn ñoà theo laân caän ñieåm vöøa nhaán chuoät

Khi ñieåm nhaán chuoät khoâng coù ñòa danh ñang hieån thò thì di chuyeån baûn ñoà vaø ngöôïc laïi thì hieån thò thoâng tin ñòa danh

Hieån thò thoâng tin ñòa danh vöøa ñöôïc choïn

Xoùa taát caû thoâng tin coù lieân quan ñeán ñòa danh vöøa ñöôïc choïn

. Chæ coù hieäu löïc khi ôû cheá ñoä Delete

. Hieån thò thoâng baùo neáu ñoàng yù xoùa thì môùi xoùa ñòa danh vaø ngöôïc laïi thì khoâng xoùa

8

Reâ chuoät

Chæ coù taùc duïng khi reâ qua treân vò trí ñòa danh ñaõ ñöôïc hieån thò treân baûn ñoà

9

  Zoom

Function FindArea(w,h,x,y)

      cX=w/2

      cY=h/2

      If cX=0 Or cY=0 Or x<0 Or y<0 Or x>=w Or y>=h Then

            FindArea = -1

            Exit Function

      End If      

      If x<=cX Then

            If y<=cY Then  

                  FindArea=0 'LEFTTOP

            Else   

                  FindArea=2 'LEFTBOTTOM

            End If

      Else

            If y<=cY Then

                  FindArea=1 'RIGHTTOP

            Else

                  FindArea=3 'RIGHTBOTTOM

            End If

      End If

End Function

 

Function Find4Neighbour(w,h,m,n,i,j,x,y,part)

      Dim area,k

      If m=0 Or n=0 Or i<0 Or i>=m Or j<0 Or j>=n Then

            Find4Neighbour=false

            Exit Function

      End If

      area=FindArea(w,h,x,y)

      If area=-1 Then

            Find4Neighbour=false

            Exit Function

      End If

      Dim     common, label   

      common=false

      label=255

      If i=0 Then

            If j=0 Then

                  label=0

            Else

                  If j=n-1 Then

                        label =1

                  Else

                        If area=1 Or area=3 Then

                              label=0

                        Else

                              label=1

                        End If

                  End If

            End If

      Else

            If i=m-1 Then

                  If j=0 Then

                        label=2

                  Else

                        If j=n-1 Then

                              label=3

                        Else

                              If area=1 Or area=3 Then

                                    label=2

                              Else

                                    label =3

                              End If

                        End If

                  End If

            Else

                  If j=0 Then

                        If area=0 Or area=1 Then

                              label=2

                        Else

                              label=0

                        End If

                  Else

                        If j=n-1 Then

                              If area=0 Or area=1 Then

                                    label=3

                              Else

                                    label=1

                              End If

                        Else

                              common=true

                        End If

                  End If

            End If

      End If

      If common Then

            Select Case area

                  Case 0

                        label=3

                  Case 1

                        label=2

                  Case 2

                        label=1

                  Case 3

                        label=0

            End Select

      End If

      Select Case label

            Case 0

                  part(0)="" & i & "_" & j    

                  part(1)="" & i & "_" & (j+1)

                  part(2)="" & (i+1) & "_" & j

                  part(3)="" & (i+1) & "_" & (j+1)

            Case 1

                  part(0)="" & i & "_" & (j-1)    

                  part(1)="" & i & "_" & j

                  part(2)="" & (i+1) & "_" & (j-1)

                  part(3)="" & (i+1) & "_" & j

            Case 2

                  part(0)="" & (i-1) & "_" & j    

                  part(1)="" & (i-1) & "_" & (j+1)

                  part(2)="" & i & "_" & j        

                  part(3)="" & i & "_" & (j+1)

            Case 3

                  part(0)="" & (i-1) & "_" & (j-1)    

                  part(1)="" & (i-1) & "_" & j

                  part(2)="" & i & "_" & (j-1)        

                  part(3)="" & i & "_" & j

                  break

            Case Else

                  Find4Neighbour= false

                  Exit Function

      End Select

      Find4Neighbour=true

End Function

 

Function Find4(m,n,i,j,part)

      If m<2 Or n<2 Or i<0 Or i>=m Or j<0 Or j>=n Then

            Find4=false

            Exit Function

      End If

      If i=m-1 Then

            If j=n-1 Then

                  part(0)="" & (i-1) & "_" & (j-1)

                  part(1)="" & (i-1) & "_" &  j

                  part(2)="" &  i    & "_" &  j-1

                  part(3)="" &  i    & "_" &  j

            Else

                  part(0)="" & (i-1) & "_" &  j

                  part(1)="" & (i-1) & "_" &  j+1

                  part(2)="" &  i    & "_" &  j

                  part(3)="" &  i    & "_" & (j+1)

            End If

      Else

            If j=n-1 Then

                  part(0)="" &  i    & "_" & (j-1)

                  part(1)="" &  i    & "_" &  j

                  part(2)="" & (i+1) & "_" & (j-1)

                  part(3)="" & (i+1) & "_" &  j

            Else

                  part(0)="" &  i    & "_" &  j

                  part(1)="" &  i    & "_" &  j+1

                  part(2)="" & (i+1) & "_" &  j

                  part(3)="" & (i+1) & "_" & (j+1)

            End If

      End If

      Find4=true

End Function

Sub FindTour(cchk,ttourSelect,lllid) 'vaøo:cchk, ttourSelect ra: lllid

                                                                  'chk=1&tourSelect=1&lid=20,30

      If cchk=0 Then

            ttourSelect=0

            lllid=""

            Exit Sub

      End If

      If 1*ttourSelect <> 0 Then

            Set conn = Server.CreateObject("ADODB.Connection")

            conn.Open Session("cnString")

            SQL="SELECT LocationID FROM LocationTours WHERE TourID=" & ttourSelect

            Set rs=Server.CreateObject("ADODB.Recordset")

            rs.Open SQL, conn

            lllid=""

            If Not rs.EOF Then

                  Do While Not rs.EOF

                        lllid=lllid & rs("LocationID") & ","

                        rs.MoveNext

                  Loop

                  length=Len(lllid)

                  If length>0 Then

                        lllid=Left(lllid,length-1)

                  End If

            End If

            rs.Close

            Set rs=Nothing

            Set conn=Nothing

      Else

            lllid=""

      End If

End Sub

function changeMouseDownPart(i,j,x0,y0) {

      xAnchor=xOld=x=findX(images,i,j,x0);

      yAnchor=yOld=y=findY(images,i,j,y0);

      jAnchor=jOld=jCur=j;

      iAnchor=iOld=iCur=i;

      return true;

}

function changeMouseUpResponse(partM) {

      window.status="";

      partM="<%=part(0,0)%>";

      if(partM=="")

            return;

      else {

            partMList=partM.split("_");

            if (partMList.length != 2)

                  return;

            else {

                  partI=0;partJ=0;

                  partI=1*partMList[0];partJ=1*partMList[1];

            }

      }

 

      xLeft=min(xAnchor,x)/<%=zoom%>;

      yTop=min(yAnchor,y)/<%=zoom%>;

      xRight=max(xAnchor,x)/<%=zoom%>;

      yBottom=max(yAnchor,y)/<%=zoom%>;

     

      iMin=min(iAnchor,iCur);

      jMin=min(jAnchor,jCur);

      iMax=max(iAnchor,iCur);

      jMax=max(jAnchor,jCur);

     

      info=""+iMin+","+jMin+","+iMax+","+jMax+":";

      info=info+xLeft+","+yTop+","+xRight+","+yBottom+":";

      info=info+widths+":"+heights+":";

      info=info+partI+":"+partJ;

      SetCookie("Coords",info,exp);

      parent.location.href="ResponseMouseUp.asp?left="+xLeft+"&top="+yTop+

            "&right="+xRight+"&bottom="+yBottom+

            "&widths="+widths+"&heights="+heights+

            "&idx="+"<%=Request.QueryString("idx")%>"+

            "&iidd=<%=iidd%>&flagedit=<%=flagedit%>";

}

            x=<%=x%>*wT;

            y=<%=y%>*hT;

           

            //kích thöôùc cuûa ñieåm hieån thò

            w=<%=w%>*wT;

            h=<%=h%>*hT;

           

            document.write("<style type='text/css'>");

            s="#layerLocate {position:absolute; left:" + x + "px; top:" +

              y + "px; width:" + w + "px; height:" + h + "px}";

            document.write(s);

            document.write("</style>");

      </script>
